messages.TRMSG_PRE_BATTLE:
What kinds of Pokémon live around
here, I wonder?
messages.TRMSG_DEFEAT:
I’m shocked!
How did I lose?
messages.TRMSG_POST_BATTLE:
I know all sorts of things about
Pokémon!Let’s see... There are males and
females, and some aren’t either!
messages.TRMSG_REMATCH:
Oh, hi! We meet again!
Have you seen any rare Pokémon?
